UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 459
1 (n) An explanation of the payment methods available and associated fees; and
2 (o) Any other information the department deems necessary to be included on
3 the tax bill.
4 (2) The form shall include the department's website address in accordance with KRS
5 133.225(2).
6 (3) The form may include a detachable stub for submitting payment of the tax.
7 (4) The department shall make the form available to all taxing districts that levy a
8 property tax on real property located within this state.
9 (5) This section does not apply to certificates of delinquency or third-party
10 purchasers.
